# 📁 **File Path (Pinned)**

```text
/NDH/Protocol/ULSP/Pins/ULSP-v2.1.pin
```

This is the correct placement because:

- All ULSP pins live under `/Protocol/ULSP/Pins/`  
- v2.1 is a **protocol pin**, not a milestone, not a parable, not a unified doc  
- It must sit adjacent to:
  - ULSP v1.7 pin  
  - ULSP v1.8 pin  
  - ULSP v1.9 pin  
  - ULSP v2.0 pin  

This preserves ULSP lineage purity.

---

# 📝 **Commit Description (Pin Registration)**

```text
Register ULSP v2.1 as a canonical pinned protocol. ULSP v2.1 integrates SEAL 
v1.0 and becomes the first ULSP version capable of participating in the NDH 
multi-layer audit engine, including dimensional coherence, MI Echo resonance, 
ADL/IADL state machine mapping, environmental calibration, and stability 
envelope verification. This pin establishes ULSP v2.1 as the official successor 
to ULSP v2.0 and anchors it within the ULSP lineage for all downstream NDH 
governance layers.
```

